{"tid":335093,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【甚麼叫絕望】地皇廣場2樓舖超低價30萬易手 舖價跌剩7.5%","createTime":"2017-07-25T10:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T12:16:00.000Z","uid":17738,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0ad6cbc98b1736c42ad28d5154dcb729a6eee1","tid":335093,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170725/large/1500973853_a2cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170725%2Flarge%2F1500973853_a2cf.jpg&h=97cea158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位處荃灣人流最勁大河道的劏場地皇廣場，不斷有蝕讓消息傳出，最新有一個商場2樓舖位，只以30萬元沽出，平絕近年拆售的劏場，原業主勁蝕逾370萬元，舖價跌剩原價7.5%。<br />\n<br />\n慘蝕舖位位於地皇廣場2樓238號舖，建築面積82方呎，實用面積41方呎，最新以超低價30萬元易手，實用呎價7,317元，呎價平過已補地價的公屋。原業主2012年以400.4萬元一手購入，現沽貨蝕370.4萬元，貶值92.5%。新買家為中華製衣有限公司，公司董事包括張譜昌，為一名醫生兼一名資深投資者，在中環及跑馬地等都有投資地舖及住宅經驗。<br />\n<br />\n上述成交已淪為近年拆售的各個劏場中，成交銀碼最低的一個舖位，亦是蝕讓幅度最大的一個，套現金額只夠買何文田新盤One Homantin一個電單車位。<br />\n<br />\n不過，要數到全港近年蝕得最甘的劏場舖位，則仍然是尖沙嘴首都廣場，1樓F148號舖，建築面積160方呎，實用面積80方呎，今年4月底以70萬元售出，實用呎價8,750元。較2013年一手作價，大幅貶值757.2萬元，勁蝕91.5%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57000680&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57000680%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170725&d=k6tLU5ag40v2dGNDhWlZkmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a2309b71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57000680%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170725&h=b2ed4887\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57000680&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170725</a>"},{"pid":"60e80ddabb129b7b0762ba37d5425310498d52e4","tid":335093,"uid":42900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim